<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset = "utf-8">
        <title>模擬考成績計算</title>
        <script language="JavaScript">
        window.onload = function time()
        {
            var btn =document.getElementById("btn");
            btn.onclick =function()
            {
                var num1 =prompt("請輸入單選題答對題數");
                num1 =num1*2;
                //var num11 = Number(num1);//為答對題數乘以題分就好
                var sum4=0;
                var sum=0;
                var num3 =prompt("請輸入多選題題數");
                var num5 =prompt("請輸入多選題題分");
                var num33 = Number(num3);
                    for(var i=1;i<=num33;i++)
                    {
                        var num2 = prompt("請輸入第"+i+"的錯誤選項數");
                        var num22 = Number(num2);
                        if(5-(2*num22)<0){
                            sum = sum +0;
                        }
                        else{
                            sum = sum +(((5-2*num22)/5)*num5);
                        }
                        sum4 =sum+num1;
                    }
                    alert("您的總分是:"+sum4);
            }
        }
        </script> 
    </head>
        <body>
            <h1>輸入規則</h1>
            <p>1.請單科輸入，目前此網頁僅供單科目成績計算</p>
            <P>2.輸入時請依照指示輸入，否則成績會有誤</P>
            <button id="btn">開始計算成績</button>
        </body>
</html>
